column1: # Let the below loc & rhymes be an object lesson: just because you *can* configure somewhat auto-generated poetry

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_01_A_010: "O how such a beautiful countenance gleams

column4: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_01_B_020: So perfectly pure I come apart at the seams
column5: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_01_B_030: Being caught in [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] smile is as warm as sunbeams
column6: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_02_A_010: That scrumptious [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomanMan] who charms me so

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_02_B_020: "Whose very face seems always to glow
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_02_B_030: To which my fealty I eternally owe
column3: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_03_A_010: I wonder what secrets [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] mask protects?"

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_03_B_020: "For surely this [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomanMan] is free of defects
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Romance_03_B_030: Is it a shield or just an affect?"

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_01_A_010: "No matter how many days twist and pass

column4: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_01_B_030: Winds whisper coldly through the grass
column5: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_02_A_010: When such beautiful countenance is hid from sight

column3: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_02_B_020: The pain surely feels a personal slight
column4: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_02_B_030: Those left behind must feel a blight
column5: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_03_A_010: How cruel a mistress is random chance

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_03_B_010: "To deprive the world of such beautiful dance
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_03_B_020: To cast [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHim] aside with nary a glance
column3: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Mourning_03_B_030: To leave us all in this cursed trance

## Legacy
 GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_01_A_010: The mightiest [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomenMen] must leave this Earth

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_01_B_020: "And hope of good words there is no dearth"
GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_01_B_030: "No matter what realms they have given birth
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_02_A_010: [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomenMen|U] need not fear as lives depart
GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_02_B_020: Crossing to quiet death with noble heart
column3: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_02_B_030: Though it may tear their grievers apart
column4: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Legacy_03_A_010: What [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomanMan] does not hope to rest when tired

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_01_B_010: "It'll ne'er find a keener set of hands
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_01_B_020: It cannot have expected this firebrand
column3: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_01_B_030: All flashes of iron and shouted demands

column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_02_B_030: [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetSheHe|U] does good business in ridding turds

### ^Edward I, bein' a lad.
 GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_03_A_010: Though conflict brings wrath to all someday

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_03_B_010: "T'is this [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomanMan]'s sword that holds death at bay
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_03_B_020: Our [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.Custom('GetHeroineHero')] lives to enter the fray!"

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Strife_03_B_030: "None are so blighted as this [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.Custom('GetHeroineHeroPossessive')] prey

## Incompetence
 GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_01_A_010: A [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetLadyLord] is nought without wisdom

column6: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_02_A_010: Some [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomenMen] simply make all others queasy

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_02_B_010: "Their appearance so poor that jokes come easy
column4: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_02_B_030: Such that no one around them can talk freely
column5: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_03_A_010: Sometimes Fate is far too cruel

column1: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_03_B_010: "Leaving noble and peasant under such rule
column2: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_03_B_020: Letting a realm become such a cesspool
column3: GeneratePoem_Intro_Rhyming_Incompetence_03_B_030: To put a [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetLadyLord]'s crown on such a mule

column1: GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Romance_01_B_030: "But to fail to try would be a bigger regret."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Romance_02_A_010: "For [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] life is my life and our life to be
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Romance_02_B_010: "The beautiful start to a family tree."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Romance_02_B_030: "As warm and refreshing as a fragrant hot tea."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Romance_03_A_010: "The mere thought of [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] smile brings one to my face
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Romance_03_B_020: "And makes my heart flutter with remarkable pace."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Mourning_01_B_030: "Who next among us will end [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] span?"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Mourning_03_A_010: "When one so great falls so far
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Mourning_03_B_020: "Are Fate's cruel whims not simply bizarre?"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Legacy_01_B_030: "So that the whole world remembers their face!"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Legacy_02_B_010: "That all they leave behind is shit."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Legacy_02_B_020: "That their deeds leave those left after split."

column2: will life echo through the years?"

column1: GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_01_B_010: "Then next to their door is [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] sword brought."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_01_B_020: "They'll learn how it is an empire is wrought."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_01_B_030: "They'll soon see on which side they have fought."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_02_A_010: "Then all shall tremble as [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetSheHe] takes field
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_02_B_010: "And show to the foe that there's no thick-enough shield."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_02_B_020: "All fire and fury and thundering wield."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_02_B_030: "[ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis|U] scything blows too harsh to heal."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_03_B_010: "Lest they discover where the last challenger went."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_03_B_020: "Unless to the hereafter they wish to be sent."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Strife_03_B_030: "Or else terrible rage shall their bodies be rent."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_01_A_010: "Oh what cruel fates Destiny doles out
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_01_B_010: "When such a tosspot wields such clout?"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_01_B_020: "When the world allows such stupidity to sprout?"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_01_B_030: "When all must behold such a terrible lout?"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_02_A_010: "When such a [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetWomanMan] is seen to exist
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_02_B_010: "It makes one want to hurl a fist!"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_02_B_020: "We all hope they get deadly cysts!"
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_03_B_010: "And all the world feels pain and ache."
GeneratePoem_Outro_Rhyming_Incompetence_03_B_020: "No bad idea enough [ROOT.Var('poem_subject').Char.GetHerHis] lust to slake."
